PrecisAuthority to sell to the MONTREAL CHINESE COMMUNITY UNITED CENTRE INC. of a land (696.75 m²) with the building situated at 211 de la Gauchetière West in Montreal, Quebec and to sell to The Corporation of the Chinese Catholic Community of Montreal a land situated at 205 de la Gauchetière West; Order in Council P.C. 1986-2929 is hereby revoked.
